<section class="testimonials">
  <div class="container reveal">
    <div class="watermark-text" aria-hidden="true">Testimonials</div>

    <div class="testimonial-content">
      <div class="header">
        <h2 class="color-primary">Hear From Our Clients</h2>
        <p>A few words from the most impactful and innovative <br/>intellectual property professionals around the world.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="quote-box">
        <blockquote>
          “Trexo has built amazing technology that gives us instant access to accurate IP Information. We are able to avoid potential issues with our IP data in a purely automated fashion. It frees up our valuable docketing staff to spend more time on their core day-to-day duties.”
        </blockquote>
        <cite>— David L., Business Owner</cite>
      </div>

      <div class="controls">
        <img src="/assets/landing-page/Website_icon/Left arrow.svg" alt="Previous" class="arrow" />
        <img src="/assets/landing-page/Website_icon/Right arrow.svg" alt="Next" class="arrow" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials {
    background-color: white;
    padding: 160px 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .watermark-text {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 5%;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    font-size: 20vw;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
    pointer-events: none;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .testimonial-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .header h2 { font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .header p { color: #666; margin-bottom: 80px; }

  blockquote {
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  cite {
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #1a1a1c;
  }

  .controls {
    margin-top: 60px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 30px;
  }

  .arrow {
    width: 40px;
    cursor: pointer;
    opacity: 0.8;
    transition: opacity 0.3s;
  }

  .arrow:hover { opacity: 1; }

  .color-primary { color: var(--color-primary); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    blockquote { font-size: 20px; }
  }
</style>
